from datetime import date, timedelta

# Function to find the last Friday of a given month and year
def last_friday(year, month):
    # Start from the last day of the month
    last_day = date(year, month + 1, 1) - timedelta(days=1)
    # Calculate the last Friday
    last_friday = last_day - timedelta(days=(last_day.weekday() - 4) % 7)
    return last_friday.day

# Get the last Friday of November 2022
last_friday_november_2022 = last_friday(2022, 11)
last_friday_november_2022
